#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.43"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.43:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.43:0.2"
msgid "5. Cūḷavagga"
msgstr "5. The Lesser Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.43:0.3"
msgid "43. Atthavasasutta"
msgstr "43. Good Reasons"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.151"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.43:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Tayo, bhikkhave, atthavase sampassamānena alameva paresaṃ dhammaṃ desetuṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, taking three reasons into consideration provides quite enough "
"motivation to teach Dhamma to another."

msgctxt "an3.43:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.43:1.3"
msgid "Yo dhammaṃ deseti so atthappaṭisaṃvedī ca hoti dhammappaṭisaṃvedī ca."
msgstr "When the teacher understands the meaning and the teaching."

msgctxt "an3.43:1.4"
msgid "Yo dhammaṃ suṇāti so atthappaṭisaṃvedī ca hoti dhammappaṭisaṃvedī ca."
msgstr "When the audience understands the meaning and the teaching."

msgctxt "an3.43:1.5"
msgid ""
"Yo ceva dhammaṃ deseti yo ca dhammaṃ suṇāti ubho atthappaṭisaṃvedino ca "
"honti dhammappaṭisaṃvedino ca."
msgstr ""
"When both the teacher and the audience understand the meaning and the "
"teaching."

msgctxt "an3.43:1.6"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo atthavase sampassamānena alameva paresaṃ dhammaṃ "
"desetun”ti."
msgstr ""
"Taking these three reasons into consideration provides quite enough "
"motivation to teach Dhamma to another.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.43:1.7"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
